title: Food Substitutes To Try This Thanksgiving | SciShow Compilation
description:
Just in time for Thanksgiving, this SciShow compilation explores the science behind food substitutes such as applesauce in place of butter,  animal-free meat, and artificial sweeteners. 

Hosted by: Stefan Chin (he/him)
